nodes.text: The Raptor Line was a fleet of ships serving the forces of Moff Kentor Sarne during the DarkStryder Campaign. The fleet served in the Battle of Kathol System and was presumably destroyed or dissolved.
The Raptor Line's flagship was the Raptor. The fleet also contained the following ships.
The fleet also had a complement of TIE/LN starfighters aboard the Raptor.
